e2df8f36-2a90-4e7f-9de6-9c5ce0ac8dc5.text:
digit = [0, 1, 2, 3, 5, 7, 8, 9]
n = input()
while n != 0:
    new_num = []
    eight = 1
    
    while eight * 8 <= n:
        eight *= 8
    while eight > 0:
        new_num.append(n / eight)
        n %= eight
        eight /= 8
    
    nn_str = ''
    for i in range(0, len(new_num)):
        nn_str += str(digit[new_num[i]])
    print nn_str
    n = input()
